cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.DS 

The paper discusses the use of neural networks for classification and regression tasks, as well as few-shot image classification tasks, which are all topics within the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), and data structures (cs.DS). The paper specifically focuses on the use of infinitely wide neural networks, which is a topic within machine learning and neural networks.
